Retrieves a list of bills for a specific user.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/bill/overview`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`userId` | Unbill user ID.


### 200 Response Body

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
`bills` | List of bills.
`bills.bill` | Bill data.
`bills.bill.balance` | Current balance.
`bills.bill.dueDate` | Current Current due date.
`bills.bill.status` | Current Status `paid, pending, upcoming, overdue, syncing`.
`bills.company` | Bill company data.
`bills.company.name` | Name of the company.
`bills.company.logo` | URL of the company logo.
`bills.company.paysRent` | Whether this company accepts rent payments (if true, the logo looks best as a background image)